.IP "\s-1JMAX\s0" 10
.IX Item "JMAX"
(output) \s-1INTEGER\s0
.Sp
The maximum value of J in the array W3J. This corresponds to the last non-zero element of W3J.
.IP "J2" 10
.IX Item "J2"
(input) \s-1INTEGER\s0
.Sp
A positive integer.
.IP "J3" 10
.IX Item "J3"
(input) \s-1INTEGER\s0
.Sp
A positive integer.
.IP "M1" 10
.IX Item "M1"
(input) \s-1INTEGER\s0
.Sp
An integer.
.IP "M2" 10
.IX Item "M2"
